  "title": "ELECTRICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong>:</p><ul><li>Install, maintain and repair electrical and related construction equipment.</li><li>Carry out day-to-day monitoring of construction equipment performance.</li><li>Perform routine maintenance of construction equipment.</li><li>Able to troubleshoot, investigate and provide service and evaluation on technical issues that arise.</li><li>Provide technical support and consultation to customers on the system and application.</li><li>Perform coordination and supervision with contractors, vendors and customers during projects implementation.</li><li>Strict adherence to Company Safety Protocols and Guidelines.</li><li>Perform housekeeping of tools and inventory parts</li><li>Perform installation and commissioning works at sites.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years relevant work experience in a similar capacity in the construction industry</li><li>Able to work independently and as a team</li><li>Ability to communicate effectively</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Adeline Tan</p><p>EA Licence Number: 23C1668</p><p>Registration Number: R23115708</p><p>Ezline Pte Ltd</p>",
